  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, it shows that there are many areas where TLP can be used with PHM to improve maintenance.",
    "Once it is established where TLP would be effective in the maintenance timeline, text processing methods compatible with the tasks can be identified.",
    "Our understanding is that text similarity methods with semantic and syntactic similarity can be very useful for a variety of tasks-matching new maintenance problems to existing problems actions to predict corrective actions, using keywords from processes to identify replacement strategies for tools/components, and several other tasks.",
    "Another suitable method for data from MWOs is Topic Modeling.",
    "It identifies the most dominant topics and keywords from maintenance problems, helping to quantify what systems/components utilizes the most resources."
